Package: beef
Version: 0.6.0.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: ruby, nodejs, git, make, clang, sqlite, openssl-tool, build-essential, curl, libcurl, ruby-nokogiri, ruby-curb
Recommends: metasploit-framework
Section: web
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://beefproject.com/
Description: Browser Exploitation Framework
 BeEF is a penetration testing tool that focuses on the web browser.
 It allows security professionals to assess the security posture of
 a target using client-side attack vectors.
